  "reference_number": "INU0407",
  "remarks": "\nNuclear Reactors Fuel Company is an involved person under the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following ground: Nuclear Reactors Fuel Company is responsible for and engaged in a relevant nuclear activity, namely the proliferation or development of nuclear weapons in, or for use in, Iran, or an activity that could lead to the development of nuclear weapons in, or for use in, Iran. \n",
